<section class="faq">
  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-question">What is RightsInfoIndia?</button>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>
        RightsInfoIndia is an opensource platform dedicated to providing
        comprehensive information about legal rights in India, helping
        individuals understand and navigate their legal entitlements
        effectively.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-question">How can I contribute to the site?</button>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>
        Firstly, thank you for considering contributing to our site! We truly
        appreciate your interest in helping us improve and expand the
        information available to our users.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can contribute by sharing your knowledge on legal matters,
        suggesting improvements to the content, or providing feedback. If you
        have expertise in specific areas of law or legal processes, we welcome
        your insights to ensure our content remains accurate and relevant.
      </p>
      <p>
        To get started, please check out our <a href="/contribute"
          >Contribution Guide</a
        >, where you'll find detailed instructions on how to submit your
        contributions, as well as guidelines on the types of content we're
        looking for. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel
        free to reach out to us.
      <p>
        Thank you again for your support and for helping us make legal
        information more accessible to everyone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #e9e9e9; 
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .faq h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--black);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .faq-item {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-question {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-align: left;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
  }
  .faq-answer {
    display: none;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: #f0f0f0;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: -1px;
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #555;
  }

  .faq-item.active .faq-answer {
    display: block;
  }
</style>

<script>
  document
    .querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>(".faq-question")
    .forEach((question) => {
      question.addEventListener("click", () => {
        const item = question.parentElement as HTMLElement;
        const answer = item.querySelector(".faq-answer") as HTMLElement;

        item.classList.toggle("active");

        if (item.classList.contains("active")) {
          answer.style.maxHeight = `${answer.scrollHeight}px`;
        } else {
          answer.style.maxHeight = "0";
        }
      });
    });
</script>
